title: GTA 6: The Biggest Leak in Gaming History - Kinda Funny Games Daily 09.19.22
description:
Greg and special guest Danielle Riendeau (formerly of Fanbyte) talk about Grand Theft Auto 6's GIGANTIC leak, Rockstar responding, Diablo IV's leak, and Cyberpunk 2077 making a comeback.  

Follow Danielle: https://twitter.com/Danielleri

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:05:48 - Housekeeping

The first two episodes of Survive Block Island: Meltdown are available right now on RoosterTeeth.com. That’s Rooster Teeth’s survival reality show taking place in Minecraft featuring names like Meg Turney, Gavin Free, Michael Jones, and the one and only Blessing Adeoye Jr. Go cheer Bless on as he tries to survive in dire conditions.

Our latest House of The Dragon screencast is up right now on Youtube.com/KindaFunny.

The Star Wars Re-Review for Rogue One has been POSTPONED so it will not be live later today for Patrons nor tomorrow on YouTube. As soon as we know, we’ll let you know the new time and place for it so we can talk about the beloved movie all together with Tim, Barrett, Anthony Carboni, and Saige Ryan!

The Roper Report  -

00:08:10 - Rockstar Confirms GTA 6 Leak, Says Development Will Not Be Affected
00:19:21 - Over 40 minutes of Diablo 4 gameplay has seemingly been leaked
00:23:09 - Cyberpunk 2077 player counts are skyrocketing
00:29:08 - Ad
00:31:15 - BREAKING: New PS5 Model Rumored
00:38:28 - Return to Monkey Island Review Round Up
00:43:22 - Fortnite’s new season adds Spider-Gwen and goopy chrome
00:47:20 - The Pokémon Company denies claims that it has issues with ‘Nuzlocke runs’
00:51:40 - Out today
00:53:00 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts: Greg & Niki Grayson (formerly of Fanbyte)
